Detailed Description

Super type for all activity media objects.

Super class for JRImageMediaObject, JRFlashMediaObject, and JRMp3MediaObject – the media objects that are shareable in JRActivityObjects. Do not subclass this object, instead instantiate one of the supplied subclasses.
